OL,3,C'Scam Van' tours Scottish Borders to
OL,4,Cprotect people becoming victims of
OL,5,Cfraud
OL,7,FResidents across the are being urged
OL,8,Fto protect themselves against scammers
OL,9,Fby visiting a so-called "Scam Van."
OL,11,FThe tour across the region has been
OL,12,Forganised by trading standards.
OL,14,FIt aims to improve how people protect
OL,15,Fthemselves, and follows the launch of
OL,16,Fthe Scottish Borders Trusted Trader
OL,17,FScheme last summer.
