OL,3,C'Scam Van' tours Scottish Borders to
OL,4,Cprotect people becoming victims of
OL,5,Cfraud
OL,7,FVisitors to the scam van can expect to
OL,8,Fbe given resources on things like how
OL,9,Fto combat rogue traders, identify
OL,10,Fscammers and deter unwanted cold
OL,11,Fcallers.
OL,13,FThere will also be the opportunity to
OL,14,Fget advice and learn where to go for
OL,15,Fhelp if needed.
OL,17,FThe tour around the region is taking
OL,18,Fplace between 20-24 May.
OL,20,FWhere will the scam van be and when?
