OL,7,FCouncillor Julie Pirone, Executive
OL,8,FMember for Communities and Culture for
OL,9,Fthe Scottish Borders said: "I am
OL,10,Fdelighted that we are empowering local
OL,11,Fpeople to take action against scammers
OL,12,Fand protect themselves through the
OL,13,Flaunch of the Scam Van Tour.
OL,15,F"This a great opportunity for
OL,16,Feveryone, no matter their age, to gain
OL,17,Fthe knowledge and tools needed to
OL,18,Fprotect ourselves against scammers and
OL,19,Ffraud which sadly is on the increase.
